### Test API Endpoints for Job Management

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Execute Command (Creates Job Entry)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "command": "ls -la /tmp"
}

### Execute Another Command
POST http://localhost:3000/api/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "command": "echo 'Hello World from remote server'"
}

### Execute Long Running Command
POST http://localhost:3000/api/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "command": "sleep 10 && echo 'Completed after 10 seconds'"
}

### Get All Jobs
GET http://localhost:3000/api/jobs

### Get Jobs with Pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/jobs?limit=10&offset=0

### Get Jobs by Status
GET http://localhost:3000/api/jobs?status=completed

### Get Job by ID (Replace with actual job ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/jobs/YOUR_JOB_ID_HERE

### Get Job Statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/jobs-stats

### Cancel Command (Replace with actual job ID)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jobId": "YOUR_JOB_ID_HERE"
}

### Delete Job (Replace with actual job ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/jobs/YOUR_JOB_ID_HERE
